{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我以復活日盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"我以自責的靈魂盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"難道人猜想我絕不能集合他的骸骨嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"不然，（我將集合他的骸骨），而且能使他的每個手指復原。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"不然，人欲長此放蕩下去。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他問復活日在甚麼時候。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"當眼目昏花，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"月亮昏暗，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"日月相合的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"在那日，人將說：「逃到哪裡去呢？」"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"絕不然，絕無任何避難所。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"在那日，唯你的主那裡，有安定之所。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"在那日，各人將被告知自己前前後後做過的事情。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"不然，各人對自己就是明証，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"即使他多方托辭。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"你不要搖動你的舌頭，以便你倉卒地誦讀它。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"集合它和誦讀它，確是我的責任。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"當我誦讀它的時候，你當靜聽我的誦讀。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"然後解釋它，也是我的責任。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"真的，你們喜愛現世的生活，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"而不顧後世的生活。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"在那日，許多面目是光華的，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"是仰視著他們的主的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"在那日，許多面目是愁苦的，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他們確信自己必遭大難。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"真的，靈魂達到鎖骨，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"有人說：「誰是祝由的？」"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他確信那是離別。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"（死時）脛與脛相纏結。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"在那日，他只被驅趕到你的主那裡。"}]}